                </div>

                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="p-1">
                        Spacing utilities control margin, padding, and gaps using a shared spacing scale.
                        They let you quickly adjust outer spacing (<code>margin</code>), inner spacing
                        (<code>padding</code>), and the gap between flex/grid items using a consistent set
                        of values and responsive breakpoints.
                    </p>

                    <p class="p-1">
                        All utilities are generated from the <code class="text-bold text-primary">$spacings</code> map
                        and the global <code class="text-bold text-primary">$breakpoints</code> configuration.
                        Margins support the <code>auto</code> value, paddings do not, and gap helpers only accept
                        numeric spacing values.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

